data.description: Nice 4 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 living and 2 dining areas with in ground pool.  Home features split bedroom arrangement, hardwood floors in den, updated kitchen with tons of cabinet space.  Vaulted ceilings with nice landscaped yard with sprinkler.  New roof in April 2015, new AC (inside and out Oct 2016), new stainless appliances with double oven in June 2015. New deck June 2018. Fresh paint inside and out including the garage. Security System.  Extra parking in back and the storage shed stays.  Nice backyard with covered patio area for entertaining and gunite pool.   $2500 carpet allowance for new carpet of your choice in the 4 bedrooms.  Check out the pictures!  325-763-3700 for a showing.
data.whatILove: Excellent neighborhood, great open space and flow to the home, tons of cabinet space, wonderful pool.  Less than $110/ft in Southland with a pool and major updates!!
